      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. Honestly, this car looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been pampered since day one\u2014always garaged and kept spotless. You won't find a single scratch or hiccup here; it\u2019s basically in perfect shape. I'm looking for someone who will love it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
