    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Offered is a concours-level E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 inline-six with crisp throttle response via individual throttle bodies and optimized VANOS timing. This specimen boasts a reinforced rear subframe and a meticulously maintained Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. Performance is enhanced by a bespoke suspension setup with adjustable compression and rebound, paired with a mechanical limited-slip differential for superior cornering exit speeds. The chassis remains rigid and free of structural fatigue, while the exterior retains its factory luster with zero clear coat degradation. Mechanically sorted with recent rod bearing service and a comprehensive cooling system overhaul, this is a turn-key collector piece for the discerning driver.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
