    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, meticulously maintained and kept in a climate-controlled garage under a soft cover when not in use. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, completely free of swirl marks, stone chips, or door dings. Every body panel is original with perfect factory gaps, and the alloy wheels are pristine with no curb rash. Inside, the cabin is showroom-fresh; the premium leather remains supple with no bolster wear or creasing, and the dashboard is free from any sun exposure or fading. All electronic components, from the high-fidelity sound system to the dual-zone climate control, function perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, featuring a comprehensive service history performed exclusively by certified technicians. The engine bay is clean enough to eat off of, and the undercarriage shows no signs of road wear or oxidation. This is a rare, collector-grade example that offers a 'new car' experience for the discerning enthusiast.",
